{"tid":1723624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲用twitter 刪舔共facebook","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T08:51:55.000Z","uid":318628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d4a924b300901d8dcd94a45f6ae2e765c3b12d","tid":1723624,"uid":318628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:43:39.000Z","msg":"舔共罪證<br />\n一路想入中國市場<br />\n與多間中國企業簽訂數據共享協議<br />\n打假無力<br />\n配合警謊 刪post <br />\n<br />\n當一個app給予你太多便利 捆綁你<br />\n就好似強國 微信咁<br />\n你給予佢既資料就越黎越多<br />\n應該係時候考慮下停用facebook <br />\n<br />\n人唔可以因貪方便而一成不變<br />\n溫水煮蛙<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔用facebook 可以睇反佢哋既網頁增加反佢地網站流量 廣告收入<br />\n唔洗俾facebook 食<br />\n<br />\n歡迎提供更多罪證及討論"},{"pid":"c734ee1091107b0a3d8cc812d0a9182f1f361b4d","tid":1723624,"uid":201992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"全世界跟我講一次<br />\n<br />\n政府答應五大訴求，才是回復平靜的最快方法。"},{"pid":"f0a477591140c1b4a989e1b8420f2a59af80edab","tid":1723624,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:45:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組會keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=e9551758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSenator Scott 幫香港人出聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senrickscott/status/1195147582609252353?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrickscott%2Fstatus%2F1195147582609252353%3Fs%3D21&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=783eeed9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrickscott%2Fstatus%2F1195147582609252353%3Fs%3D21&h=37d03fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senrick